{"tid":975810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊岳橋大婚之喜, 多名保皇同事出席歡喜宴會同台合照, 同賀人生大事","createTime":"2019-01-10T03:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T02:02:53.000Z","uid":51701,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"581fe45d9b8880b63be131e2d801e99762184475","tid":975810,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:11:23.000Z","msg":"立法會議員楊岳橋早前於Facebook自爆婚訊，3個月後終於設酒會招待一眾議員。立法會目前雖正就修改《議事規則》一事而火花四起，但酒會初段所到臨的議員以建制派議員為多，包括立法會主席梁君彥，莫非楊岳橋與建制派關係較佳？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n酒會今天(8日)黃昏舉行，與立會財務委員會會議同步進行，不少建制派議員早就到場送上祝福，包括議員鍾國斌、張宇人、盧偉國、梁美芬等，反而泛民議員於酒會稍後時間才陸續到場，並且逗留時間較長。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打了紅色領呔的楊岳橋，與穿紅裙的太太相襯，應眾人要求下於橄欖枝布景下多次親吻。楊岳橋透露，聖誕期間將赴意大利度蜜月，惟因會議問題，兩人並非同步出發，他笑稱希望能如期出發，毋須因會議拖延至要改機票。"},{"pid":"56a1cdad598f37943487533e4582a16d109f0cd7","tid":975810,"uid":110832,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:12:42.000Z","msg":"自己人"},{"pid":"0139860beb6185dd57972f649da8f0225089c049","tid":975810,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbb4d0f33c68e429cb471a072ffa1c39c6165c4","tid":975810,"uid":51701,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQx4-KTgHYhepn58R8CUW8opsQseUxSCWhunvz6SwTFEIgkyIb1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcQx4-KTgHYhepn58R8CUW8opsQseUxSCWhunvz6SwTFEIgkyIb1&h=b8e79503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢老婆個樣都乏善可陳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n酒會又比人地抽水<br />\n希望可以搞得再好啲"},{"pid":"1a875bce3fbeff702d382d261ce2b12530687345","tid":975810,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"edbb4d0f33c68e429cb471a072ffa1c39c6165c4","tid":975810,"uid":51701,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"reply